item.title: Dumpsterdive podcast episode 1
item.description: Welcome to Dumpsterdive podcast (sorry this cast i used my free program insted to make the cast so there were voice over ads my next cast will not have this) I used to own a cd store and these are songs I pulled out of boxes for you to enjoy...rare britpop indie singles music from St. Etienne Erasure Lush Prefab Sprout Suede Terry Hall Julian Cope Aztec Camera
